impactDescription:
Organised meet-ups to create awareness of crypto and optimism at large. 
Hosted campaigns in various cities in my country, some of which included house to house, door to door, office to office, recreation to recreation centers.
Not to forget, I also visited schools, college and university students who are ICT oriented and looking to explore the sphere of crypto and optimism network at large. 

These are a few and more to come from me.

Thanks for the opportunity to do more
